{"tid":1733050,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民族要向敵人展現勇氣","createTime":"2019-11-18T04:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T12:03:17.000Z","uid":331949,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db7385e85369498fd7bb28daae18d2a7ebc80c61","tid":1733050,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"香港，願意萬人行紅隧救我地嘅兒女嗎？<br />\n<br />\n唔係要和理非式感覺良好打飛機，但亦唔可以認輸。輸，你就輸一世。要有不怕死嘅精神，展現氣勢、反抗、力量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sAfZRJP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsAfZRJP.jpg&h=5dae0a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">V</span>"},{"pid":"5d63c9fddd5bc1405520cdd9ae042f5520ba99ab","tid":1733050,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:29:40.000Z","msg":"梁天琦 各有各做 論：你認為勇武抗爭有效，繼續勇武抗爭。和理非有效，繼續和理非。道德感召有效，做道德人。國際戰線有效，出國遊說。所謂兄弟爬山，各自努力，堅持做自己認為啱嘅事，並包容體諒其他手足，就算佢地嘅方法同你唔同。"},{"pid":"f683c9c655a63d05c998c4e5d3d95a0857e14388","tid":1733050,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"睇過Dunkirk未？香港人，係時候做一個自由嘅人。"},{"pid":"0215832f52c1cd66e7f9c771b0dfbd6611b1a54a","tid":1733050,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:37:17.000Z","msg":"浪漫主義唔一定係壞，行動都可以好浪漫。如果一萬個人行入紅隧作集體公民抗命，浪漫嗎？<br />\n<br />\n現今浪漫主義之弊病源於其流於表面言語，不以實際行動體現。"},{"pid":"d5e511f5ce166110be782e9762a9eaa2eb5b168d","tid":1733050,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:49:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kPFf1TF8QNo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkPFf1TF8QNo&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2QmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=ec33ff1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kPFf1TF8QNo</a><br />\n<br />\n香港兒女，要智取；出其不意。共勉"},{"pid":"79b85cdb1ea0c8e8b4961c8d6f618dc146129674","tid":1733050,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我大佬Winston Churchill"},{"pid":"6c8790847a3255056f378888b8ec8418440adf3a","tid":1733050,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79b85cdb1ea0c8e8b4961c8d6f618dc146129674","tid":1733050,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我大佬Winston Churchill"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:03:17.000Z","msg":"都係我大佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}